      <Value><![CDATA[New Adventures Are Coming]]></Value>
    </newsTitle>
    <newsExcerpt>
      <Value><![CDATA[Pack your bags — new islands, new characters, and new stories are coming to Cow Paradise soon.]]></Value>
    </newsExcerpt>
    <newsBody>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Big things are on the horizon. We're expanding the Cow Paradise universe with two brand-new islands, a third generation of Moo Family characters, and a special storytelling season.</p><p>Sign up for the newsletter to be the first to know.</p>]]></Value>
